---
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";
import heroImage from "assets/hero.png";
import Link from "@components/ui/link.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
---

<main
  class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 place-items-center pt-16 pb-8 md:pt-12 md:pb-24">
  <div class="py-6 md:order-1 hidden md:block">
    <Picture
      src={heroImage}
      alt="Astronaut in the air"
      widths={[200, 400, 600]}
      sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 620px"
      loading="eager"
      format="avif"
    />
  </div>
  <div>
    <span
      class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter">
      Analisa pasar pangan melalui 
      <span class="animate-text bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 via-purple-500 to-orange-500 bg-clip-text 
      text-transparent text-7xl font-black">
      Integrasi Data.</span>
  </span>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-xl">
      Bosan dengan data pasar yang ribet? PasarKu hadir sebagai solusi SaaS cerdas, 
      mengintegrasikan data pasar pangan real-time dengan dashboard intuitif.
      <wbr         /> 
      Kelola bisnis Anda dengan mudah dan optimalkan strategi pasar Anda.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
      <Link
        href="#"
        href="/about"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex gap-1 items-center justify-center"
        rel="noopener">
        <!-- <Icon class="text-white w-5 h-5" name="bx:bxs-cloud-download" /> -->

         Pelajari Selengkapnya
      </Link>
      <Link
        size="lg"
        style="outline"
        rel="noopener"
        href="https://panelharga.badanpangan.go.id/"
        class="flex gap-1 items-center justify-center"
        target="_blank">
        <Icon class="text-black w-4 h-4" name="bx:bxs-data" />
         Sumber Data
      </Link>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
